---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import FAQ from '../components/FAQ.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="POE2 Trade Guide: Complete Trading System for Path of Exile 2"
  description="Master POE2 trade with our comprehensive guide. Learn currency exchange, item trading, and advanced trading techniques for Path of Exile 2."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <Hero />
    
    <!-- Attention Section -->
    <Section
      title="Why Trading Matters in Path of Exile 2"
      id="why-trading"
    >
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Evolution of POE2 Trade System</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            The POE2 trade system represents a revolutionary step forward in the Path of Exile franchise. Building upon years of community feedback, the new trading mechanics offer streamlined interactions while maintaining the game's core economic principles. Players can now engage in more efficient trading without sacrificing the depth that made POE2 trade a cornerstone of the game's economy.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Currency Exchange vs Item Trading</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            In POE2 trade, players can engage in two primary forms of trading: direct currency exchange and item trading. The currency system remains the backbone of the economy, with various orbs and shards serving as the medium of exchange. Item trading has been enhanced with improved search filters and a more intuitive interface, making it easier to find exactly what you need.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Impact on Your Character's Progress</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Mastering POE2 trade is crucial for efficient character progression. Through trading, players can acquire essential gear upgrades, rare crafting materials, and valuable currency items that might take countless hours to find through regular gameplay. This system enables diverse build experimentation and faster endgame progression.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <img 
            src="/images/trade-system.webp" 
            alt="POE2 Trade System Interface"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-xl"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Interest Section -->
    <Section
      title="Key Features of POE2 Trade"
      id="features"
      className="bg-gray-50"
    >
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">In-Game Trading System</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              The new POE2 trade system features an intuitive in-game interface that allows for seamless trading between players. With improved chat functionality and trade notifications, you'll never miss an important trade opportunity. The system includes built-in price verification and item inspection tools to ensure safe trading.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Official POE2 Trade Site</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              The official POE2 trade site has been completely redesigned with advanced search capabilities, real-time listings, and integrated price checking tools. Players can easily filter items by specific modifiers, price ranges, and seller online status.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Currency Exchange Interface</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              A dedicated currency exchange interface makes converting between different currency types more straightforward than ever. Real-time exchange rates and bulk trading options help players make informed decisions about their trades.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Premium Stash Tab Trading</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Premium stash tabs now offer enhanced functionality for POE2 trade, including automatic price updating, bulk selling tools, and integrated analytics to help you price your items competitively.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Desire Section -->
    <Section
      title="How to Master POE2 Trade"
      id="how-to-trade"
      className="bg-gray-50"
    >
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Using the Trade Site Effectively</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            The POE2 trade site offers powerful search capabilities that every trader should master. Using the fuzzy search feature with the tilde (~) symbol helps find items even when you're unsure of exact names. For example, searching for "~res fire" will show all fire resistance items. The POE2 trade interface allows for precise filtering of item modifiers, making it easier to find exactly what you need.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Advanced Search Techniques</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            To optimize your POE2 trade experience, utilize the weighted sum feature for complex searches. This advanced tool helps find items with specific combinations of modifiers, perfect for finding gear upgrades. The bulk exchange section streamlines currency trading, allowing for efficient conversion of resources in the POE2 trade economy.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Market Analysis and Pricing</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Success in POE2 trade requires understanding market values. Use the live search feature to monitor price trends and catch good deals. The trade site's price checking tools help ensure fair transactions. Remember to consider both the currency exchange rates and item demand when setting prices in the POE2 trade system.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Trading Best Practices</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gray-600">
                Always verify item properties before completing a POE2 trade transaction. The new trading interface includes built-in verification tools to prevent scams.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gray-600">
                Use premium stash tabs to list items efficiently. The POE2 trade system automatically indexes these tabs, making your items visible to potential buyers instantly.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-gray-600">
                Follow trading etiquette: respond promptly to trade requests, price items fairly, and maintain a good reputation in the POE2 trade community.
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
            <h4 class="font-bold mb-4">Pro Trading Tips</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li>• Use live searches for rare items in the POE2 trade system</li>
              <li>• Learn common currency exchange rates</li>
              <li>• Keep track of market trends</li>
              <li>• Build a network of reliable trading partners</li>
              <li>• Utilize trade companion tools for efficiency</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Action Section -->
    <Section
      title="Getting Started with POE2 Trade"
      id="getting-started"
      className="bg-gray-50"
    >
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Step-by-Step Trading Guide</h3>
          <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4">
            <li>Set up your premium stash tabs</li>
            <li>Learn to use the trade site search filters</li>
            <li>Understand currency exchange rates</li>
            <li>Master the in-game trading interface</li>
            <li>Start with small trades to build experience</li>
          </ol>

          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="#" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
              Start Trading Now
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Essential Trading Tools</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              Premium Stash Tabs
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              Price Checking Tools
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              Trade Companion Apps
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <FAQ />

    <!-- Additional Resources -->
    <Section
      title="Additional Resources"
      id="resources"
    >
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Useful Trading Tools</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">POE2 Trade Companion</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Price Check Tool</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Market Analyzer</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Community Trading Guides</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Beginner's Trading Guide</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Advanced Trading Strategies</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Currency Flipping Guide</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Official POE2 Trade Links</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Official Trade Site</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Trading Forum</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Support Center</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
